OL,3,CHuw Edwards paid more than #475,000 by
OL,4,CBBC before resignation
OL,6,FThe BBC paid Huw Edwards more than
OL,7,F#475,000 last year before he resigned
OL,8,Fand left the corporation following the
OL,9,Fexplicit photos furore.
OL,11,FHis resignation in April followed
OL,12,Fallegations that he paid a young
OL,13,Fperson for sexually explicit photos.
OL,15,FThe veteran newsreader was paid
OL,16,Fbetween #475,000 and #479,999 for the
OL,17,Fyear 2023/24 for 160 presenting days,
OL,18,FBBC One news specials, election
OL,19,Fspecials and other television
OL,20,Fprogramming, according to the BBC's
OL,21,Fannual report.
