OL,6,FThis marked an increase from 2022/23,
OL,7,Fwhen he was paid between #435,000 and
OL,8,F439,999 for 180 days presenting on BBC
OL,9,FOne, as well as news specials.
OL,11,FEdwards was absent from screens from
OL,12,Fwhen the story first broke in July
OL,13,F2023 until his exit in April 2024.
OL,15,FHe was suffering from serious mental
OL,16,Fhealth issues and received in-patient
OL,17,Fhospital care.
