OL,6,FThe BBC confirmed at the time of his
OL,7,Fdeparture that he had not received a
OL,8,Fpay-off and was leaving "on the basis
OL,9,Fof medical advice from his doctors".
OL,11,FHe had long been a fixture in the
OL,12,Fcoverage of major political and royal
OL,13,Fevents, announcing Queen Elizabeth
OL,14,FII's death on the BBC and presenting
OL,15,Fcoverage of her funeral.
OL,17,FHe also anchored the BBC's broadcast
OL,18,Fof the King's coronation last year.
