OL,6,FHe was the third highest-paid employee
OL,7,Fon the 2023/24 list, up from fourth
OL,8,Flast year, which was once again topped
OL,9,Fby Match Of The Day anchor Gary
OL,10,FLineker, whose salary remained
OL,11,Funchanged at between #1,350,000 and
OL,12,F#1,354,999.
OL,14,FThis is the seventh consecutive year
OL,15,FLineker has topped the list and he
OL,16,Fcontinues to be the only star paid
OL,17,Fmore than #1 million.
