OL,6,FThe salaries of many of the BBCs most
OL,7,Ffamous faces are not disclosed on the
OL,8,Flist because the corporation does not
OL,9,Fhave to reveal the salaries of people
OL,10,Fwho are paid through production
OL,11,Fcompanies, including the BBC's
OL,12,Fcommercial arm BBC Studios.
OL,14,FThis means ubiquitous presenters and
OL,15,Fpersonalities such as Michael
OL,16,FMcIntyre, Lord Sugar, Bradley Walsh
OL,17,Fand Alex Jones do not feature.
